[Waiting for their emergency team colleagues
before having supper]

00:19:40.230 --> 00:19:42.770
They're still waiting. It takes a long time.

00:19:43.180 --> 00:19:45.980
[Moon Byungjoon: Isn't (the restaurant)
open till midnight?]

00:19:45.980 --> 00:19:49.070
[Moon Byungjoon: Then (the emergency team)
just have to get back by 11:30 PM.]

00:19:49.070 --> 00:19:51.870
[Moon Byungjoon: As long as they get back
by 11:30 PM, they can eat it.]

00:19:52.040 --> 00:19:55.050
[Lee Kang-in: It'd be nice if
the emergency team get to eat this too.]

00:19:55.050 --> 00:19:55.970
Yes.

00:19:56.070 --> 00:19:59.540
[Hoping they'll come and get a warm meal today]

00:19:59.920 --> 00:20:02.090
[They... They haven't tried
the Dubai chewy puffs?]

00:20:02.140 --> 00:20:02.200
No, not yet.

00:20:02.200 --> 00:20:02.640
[(Right, my Dubai chewy puffs!)]

00:20:02.640 --> 00:20:03.140
It's the last dish.

00:20:03.140 --> 00:20:04.280
It's the last one, the finale.

00:20:04.280 --> 00:20:05.180
Because it's the dessert.

00:20:05.180 --> 00:20:07.120
[Go Younjung: They'd eat
the dessert last, right?]

00:20:07.500 --> 00:20:07.600
[Full of expectations]

00:20:07.600 --> 00:20:08.460
I'm so curious.

00:20:09.110 --> 00:20:11.170
[Jo Seondeok: My kids would love it
if I brought (the Dubai chewy puff) home.]

00:20:11.170 --> 00:20:11.790
I know.

00:20:12.090 --> 00:20:13.460
[Jo Seondeok: It's so hard
to buy Dubai chewy cookies.]

00:20:13.460 --> 00:20:14.500
-Yeah, Dubai chewy cookies. -Yeah.

00:20:14.500 --> 00:20:15.760
[First to try the Dubai chewy puff]

00:20:15.760 --> 00:20:18.610
Unless you queue up early in the morning,
you can't buy it.

00:20:18.610 --> 00:20:21.660
[Finishes it in two bites]

00:20:22.190 --> 00:20:25.030
[Is the Dubai chewy puff good?] [Yes.]

00:20:25.200 --> 00:20:27.150
-It's delicious. -Is there cream inside?

00:20:27.150 --> 00:20:27.900
[The Dubai chewy puff is the best.]

00:20:27.900 --> 00:20:28.830
-Really? -Yeah.

00:20:29.710 --> 00:20:31.760
[(I'll try it too)]

00:20:32.550 --> 00:20:36.060
[A 119 report has been received.]

00:20:36.150 --> 00:20:36.530
A 119 report has been received.

00:20:36.530 --> 00:20:39.610
[The dispatch alarm suddenly rings]

00:20:39.990 --> 00:20:41.590
[But I haven't eaten my Dubai chewy puff.]

00:20:41.910 --> 00:20:43.020
[My puff... (sad)]

00:20:43.680 --> 00:20:44.160
A 119 report has been received.

00:20:44.160 --> 00:20:46.970
[In face of unexpected situations]

00:20:47.160 --> 00:20:47.470
I think they're leaving. Aren't they leaving?

00:20:47.470 --> 00:20:49.990
[Widespread panic]

00:20:49.990 --> 00:20:50.620
Really?

00:20:51.430 --> 00:20:51.990
Oh my... Gosh...

00:20:51.990 --> 00:20:54.460
[Hmm? Huh?]

00:20:59.690 --> 00:20:59.890
Fire dispatch! Fire dispatch!

00:20:59.890 --> 00:21:01.700
[Fire dispatch]

00:21:02.030 --> 00:21:03.510
[They're the fire team...]

00:21:03.510 --> 00:21:05.860
[Aren't they the fire team? They are!]

00:21:06.090 --> 00:21:07.750
[Hearing the report]

00:21:07.750 --> 00:21:09.640
[Running]

00:21:10.120 --> 00:21:14.640
[Firefighters rush out
before finishing their meal]

00:21:17.610 --> 00:21:20.320
[The cafeteria is empty in an instant]

00:21:20.780 --> 00:21:24.170
[The fire suppression team is on the move]

00:21:24.500 --> 00:21:25.940
[The incident command team is on the move]

00:21:26.080 --> 00:21:27.680
[The fire investigation team is on the move]

00:21:33.190 --> 00:21:38.620
[Rushing to the scene immediately]

00:21:39.690 --> 00:21:45.360
[Flustered at the sudden turn of events]

00:21:46.080 --> 00:21:46.660
Please.

00:21:49.630 --> 00:21:51.610
-They left in the middle of eating. -Yeah.

00:21:51.610 --> 00:21:52.960
What about the leftover food?

00:21:52.960 --> 00:21:55.940
[Hong Jinkyung: At least they finished.
They were nearly done eating.]

00:21:55.940 --> 00:21:57.610
[Kim Dohoon: Will they come back?]

00:21:58.690 --> 00:22:00.830
[Wait, they didn't eat the Dubai chewy puffs!]

00:22:00.830 --> 00:22:02.060
Oh no.

00:22:02.100 --> 00:22:02.590
-They left in the middle of eating. -Yeah.

00:22:02.590 --> 00:22:03.740
[(Sad)]

00:22:03.740 --> 00:22:04.850
What about the leftover food?

00:22:04.850 --> 00:22:04.950
[All by itself...]

00:22:04.950 --> 00:22:06.040
Will they come back soon?

00:22:06.040 --> 00:22:07.440
Will they come back soon?

00:22:08.080 --> 00:22:10.740
[The dispatch alarm rings again]

00:22:10.880 --> 00:22:11.820
Was it canceled?

00:22:14.210 --> 00:22:15.880
[Fire dispatch! Fire dispatch!]

00:22:16.270 --> 00:22:17.900
[Not a cancellation but another dispatch]

00:22:17.900 --> 00:22:19.600
We should clear those.

00:22:19.610 --> 00:22:20.220
There's no one here.

00:22:20.220 --> 00:22:20.730
[Taking the chance to clear the tables
while everyone is gone]

00:22:20.730 --> 00:22:21.430
Quickly.

00:22:25.280 --> 00:22:26.840
[They all didn't get to
eat the Dubai chewy puffs. (sad)]

00:22:26.840 --> 00:22:27.780
What should we do with the Dubai chewy puffs

00:22:27.780 --> 00:22:28.600
[No one but 1 person ate the Dubai chewy puff]

00:22:28.600 --> 00:22:29.860
that weren't touched?

00:22:30.150 --> 00:22:31.280
They're good as new.

00:22:38.820 --> 00:22:38.970
Only the puffs weren't eaten. They're still new.

00:22:38.970 --> 00:22:42.020
It seems they all saved the dessert for last]

00:22:49.670 --> 00:22:51.310
[Clean up the tableware and cooking utensils too]

00:22:51.310 --> 00:22:52.080
Give it to me.

00:22:57.480 --> 00:23:00.340
[Dohoon is untying the bags of noodles]

00:23:00.950 --> 00:23:05.430
[A step that took up too much time when
they were cooking for their first customers]

00:23:06.010 --> 00:23:09.430
[Preparing in advance to shorten time]

00:23:09.870 --> 00:23:11.490
-Are you untying the bags? -Yes.

00:23:11.490 --> 00:23:12.840
[Nice, nice.]

00:23:13.140 --> 00:23:17.320
[Meticulous preparation for the next dish]

00:23:18.780 --> 00:23:20.240
This is cooked perfectly.

00:23:21.610 --> 00:23:24.520
[Drinks hot soup to replenish energy]

00:23:25.150 --> 00:23:27.870
[Ah! It's really delicious!]

00:23:29.090 --> 00:23:30.920
[Hahahaha.]

00:23:31.350 --> 00:23:33.600
[A dignified man who knows
to have a leisurely cup of soup]

00:23:33.600 --> 00:23:34.260
Delicious.

00:23:35.740 --> 00:23:36.840
[Younjung: Are these the leftovers?]

00:23:36.840 --> 00:23:37.620
This one...

00:23:37.760 --> 00:23:38.700
[I'll eat it.]

00:23:38.700 --> 00:23:40.720
[Me... Me too.]

00:23:41.110 --> 00:23:41.870
[Unexpected time for a sugar fix]

00:23:41.870 --> 00:23:43.270
These are all leftovers.

00:23:44.260 --> 00:23:44.390
This one's big.

00:23:44.390 --> 00:23:49.440
[Taking care of the rest of the Dubai chewy puffs]

00:23:49.640 --> 00:23:51.090
-Did you eat it in one go? -Yeah.

00:23:54.070 --> 00:23:55.310
[A big bite]

00:23:57.700 --> 00:23:58.370
Is it good?

00:23:59.780 --> 00:24:00.220
[Especially delicious when you're tired]

00:24:00.220 --> 00:24:01.280
This is crazy good.

00:24:03.100 --> 00:24:05.130
[(Frown of approval)]

00:24:05.390 --> 00:24:07.070
[Jung Hae-in: It's way better
than the last batch.]

00:24:07.070 --> 00:24:09.170
[Yoon Namno: It's upgraded.]
[Much better.]

00:24:09.370 --> 00:24:09.600
And the rice cake...

00:24:09.600 --> 00:24:10.820
[The chewy rice cake they added is the kick]

00:24:10.820 --> 00:24:11.870
The rice cake at the end.

00:24:11.870 --> 00:24:13.860
The rice cake's really the cherry on top.

00:24:13.860 --> 00:24:16.140
[Go Younjung: It tastes much better with
cherry jam than strawberry jam.]

00:24:16.140 --> 00:24:17.200
-Cherry jam? -Yes.

00:24:17.840 --> 00:24:18.490
The cherry jam is so good.

00:24:18.490 --> 00:24:19.430
[Can't stop eating]

00:24:19.430 --> 00:24:20.790
The sour taste gives it oomph,

00:24:20.790 --> 00:24:22.120
so that it isn't boring.

00:24:22.630 --> 00:24:23.630
[Yoon Namno: Please change your masks.]

00:24:23.630 --> 00:24:24.430
-Yes. -Here.

00:24:25.050 --> 00:24:29.920
[Tidying up while they have a break]

00:24:30.070 --> 00:24:31.890
[Myungsoo.]
[Yes, yes.]

00:24:35.370 --> 00:24:35.640
[Care (?) with a hug from behind,
sweeter than Dubai chewy puffs]

00:24:35.640 --> 00:24:36.460
Thank you.

00:24:37.030 --> 00:24:38.380
I'll clean your ears for you later.

00:24:38.380 --> 00:24:39.030
Why?

00:24:39.500 --> 00:24:40.830
You have so much earwax.

00:24:42.960 --> 00:24:45.730
[The order bell suddenly rings]

00:24:45.730 --> 00:24:46.660
Is someone here?

00:24:46.930 --> 00:24:47.860
2... 2 people...

00:24:47.980 --> 00:24:49.040
How many are there?

00:24:49.340 --> 00:24:49.840
2 people...

00:24:49.840 --> 00:24:51.510
No, wait.

00:24:53.110 --> 00:24:55.260
4, 5, 6, 7...

00:24:55.780 --> 00:24:56.040
Get 7 burners ready.

00:24:56.040 --> 00:24:57.340
[7 fires.]

00:24:57.530 --> 00:24:57.550
[Urgent]

00:24:57.550 --> 00:24:59.550
This is no joke. They suddenly came.

00:24:59.700 --> 00:25:03.660
[7 rescue team members have entered]

00:25:03.880 --> 00:25:05.750
[Please take a seat and wait.]

00:25:05.950 --> 00:25:07.230
[Hahaha.]

00:25:07.810 --> 00:25:10.730
[10:10 PM:
7 rescue team members have entered]

00:25:11.130 --> 00:25:12.810
[Yoon Namno: 7 servings of noodles in total.]

00:25:12.810 --> 00:25:14.640
[Yoon Namno: Divide them into 4 and 3.]

00:25:15.040 --> 00:25:16.460
[Heating two pans]

00:25:17.900 --> 00:25:21.650
[Starts to pan-fry 7 beef patties]

00:25:22.060 --> 00:25:22.200
[4 baskets of noodles are also being cooked]

00:25:22.200 --> 00:25:23.600
Turn up the heat a little.

00:25:24.470 --> 00:25:25.680
[7 people?]

00:25:26.430 --> 00:25:29.930
[Miss Hong quietly
fills the rice bowls in the corner]

00:25:29.950 --> 00:25:32.050
[Yoon Namno: Jinkyung, scoop seven bowls.
You're free to do it, right?]

00:25:32.370 --> 00:25:34.250
[7 bowls of what?]
[Of rice.]

00:25:34.250 --> 00:25:35.000
I've already done it.

00:25:35.000 --> 00:25:37.010
[7 bowls of rice are ready]

00:25:37.060 --> 00:25:37.390
-You have? Woah. -Yes.

00:25:37.390 --> 00:25:38.890
[Reliable!]

00:25:39.320 --> 00:25:41.120
[Kim Daejoong: Good job, guys.
It's been cold today.]

00:25:41.170 --> 00:25:41.390
Yes, good job, everyone.

00:25:41.390 --> 00:25:43.520
[Exhausted...]

00:25:43.660 --> 00:25:45.560
[Kim Daejoong: Just a case of icicles
took the whole afternoon.]

00:25:45.560 --> 00:25:47.450
[Choi Jongin: (The icicles) were
more frozen than expected.]

00:25:47.730 --> 00:25:47.780
Watching from below,
while you were scraping it off up there,

00:25:47.780 --> 00:25:49.680
[Due to the sudden drop in temperature,
they've been removing icicles all day]

00:25:49.680 --> 00:25:51.940
it didn't look like you progressed much.

00:25:51.990 --> 00:25:52.200
It took so long.

00:25:52.200 --> 00:25:54.070
[Kim Daejoong: Didn't your back hurt just now?]

00:25:54.070 --> 00:25:55.870
-My back hurts a lot. -Right?

00:25:56.180 --> 00:25:58.590
[Kim Daejoong: You've to tie (the rope)
properly so your back doesn't hurt.]

00:25:58.710 --> 00:25:58.960
Because you have to put in more strength,
the center of gravity shifts back.

00:25:58.960 --> 00:26:03.460
[Exhausted after all the intensive work]

00:26:03.860 --> 00:26:05.470
[It's said to be a nutritious meal.]

00:26:05.800 --> 00:26:07.560
[Good that I didn't eat instant noodles.]
[I know, right?]

00:26:07.850 --> 00:26:09.900
[I planned to go crazy (?) at this meal today.]

00:26:10.290 --> 00:26:14.270
[Show us! Let loose today.]

00:26:14.580 --> 00:26:18.350
[Kim Daejoong: Better not have a dispatch now.]
[Please, no dispatches right now.]

00:26:18.730 --> 00:26:22.340
[Kim Daejoong: I'm going to empty my mind.
Every time we say stuff like this, it comes true.]

00:26:22.620 --> 00:26:24.980
[Don't they say humans are animals who grow?]

00:26:25.580 --> 00:26:28.060
[Left hand: cooking noodles]
[Right hand: shaking noodles]

00:26:28.680 --> 00:26:31.760
[He's controlling the heat with both hands]

00:26:32.020 --> 00:26:33.810
[Perfect teamwork]
[When will the noodles be ready?]

00:26:33.810 --> 00:26:34.870
[Perfect teamwork]
[In 10 seconds.]

00:26:34.870 --> 00:26:35.670
In 10 seconds?

00:26:36.300 --> 00:26:38.450
[It's better to cook it a bit more.]

00:26:38.890 --> 00:26:40.110
[Wait a minute.]

00:26:40.600 --> 00:26:41.740
[Gradually grasps the feeling of
when the noodles are cooked well]

00:26:41.740 --> 00:26:42.410
Done, done.

00:26:43.840 --> 00:26:45.110
[Slips in]

00:26:45.420 --> 00:26:47.120
[Hae-in, you're cooking them so well.]

00:26:47.590 --> 00:26:48.510
[Golden brown]

00:26:48.510 --> 00:26:49.310
So beautiful.

00:26:49.820 --> 00:26:50.240
Thank you.

00:26:50.240 --> 00:26:50.380
[As everyone is basking in the joy of growth]

00:26:50.380 --> 00:26:51.570
Looks like a full moon.

00:26:51.570 --> 00:26:52.250
Thank you.

00:26:53.480 --> 00:26:54.420
[Put the chicken with me.]

00:26:54.420 --> 00:26:54.940
What?

00:26:55.020 --> 00:26:56.370
Put the chicken when the noodles

00:26:56.370 --> 00:26:57.000
are out.

00:26:57.000 --> 00:26:59.810
[You never taught me this!]
[Namno: If you have 2 hands, you can do it.]

00:27:00.100 --> 00:27:00.410
Put them like this.

00:27:00.410 --> 00:27:02.880
[Mr. Park, who dislikes rapid growth]

00:27:03.240 --> 00:27:04.980
[You haven't taught me this...]
[A bit more.]

00:27:05.050 --> 00:27:06.050
[Yes, Chef!]

00:27:06.050 --> 00:27:06.810
OK, good.

00:27:07.600 --> 00:27:07.650
Are the 4 bowls ready? Move them here.

00:27:07.650 --> 00:27:09.240
[Takes the noodle soup]

00:27:10.020 --> 00:27:10.840
[Garnishes tossed to him
as soon as he puts down the bowl]

00:27:10.840 --> 00:27:11.500
Red chilis.

00:27:12.580 --> 00:27:13.750
Give me the red chilis.

00:27:13.750 --> 00:27:14.020
-You want me to do it? -Yes.

00:27:14.020 --> 00:27:15.040
[Whining while doing everything as instructed]

00:27:15.040 --> 00:27:15.950
You never taught me this!

00:27:15.950 --> 00:27:16.610
This one...

00:27:16.990 --> 00:27:17.040
[It's me, Mr. 10 Jobs]

00:27:17.040 --> 00:27:17.710
Like this?

00:27:17.780 --> 00:27:19.110
OK. Done.

00:27:20.230 --> 00:27:22.690
OK, now let's get to it for real. Do a neat job.

00:27:23.230 --> 00:27:23.240
You need to get the rice ready, Ma'am.

00:27:23.240 --> 00:27:24.520
[While whining non-stop]

00:27:24.520 --> 00:27:25.090
You do it.

00:27:25.200 --> 00:27:25.980
Now I'm doing it.

00:27:25.980 --> 00:27:26.270
Whoever is free can do it.

00:27:26.270 --> 00:27:27.530
[His hands are working obediently]

00:27:27.530 --> 00:27:29.750
It's so busy
I can't cope even if I have 10 of me!

00:27:29.750 --> 00:27:31.080
[Set the cutlery]

00:27:31.080 --> 00:27:32.900
[Plate the kimchi]

00:27:32.900 --> 00:27:34.290
[Set the rice]

00:27:34.290 --> 00:27:34.560
[Move the knife-cut noodles]

00:27:34.560 --> 00:27:35.490
Give it to me now.

00:27:35.800 --> 00:27:36.120
[Move the beef patties]

00:27:36.120 --> 00:27:37.120
The beef patties.

00:27:37.800 --> 00:27:39.740
[Add the noodle garnishes]

00:27:39.740 --> 00:27:40.590
Red chilis.

00:27:40.840 --> 00:27:41.640
[Untie the bags of noodles]

00:27:41.640 --> 00:27:42.790
A total of 7 servings of noodles.

00:27:42.790 --> 00:27:44.690
[Plate the beef patties]

00:27:44.690 --> 00:27:45.010
[Clean up the surroundings]

00:27:45.010 --> 00:27:46.380
Put these away?

00:27:47.000 --> 00:27:49.170
[Do the dishes]

00:27:49.170 --> 00:27:50.180
Move. I need to work.

00:27:50.180 --> 00:27:51.130
I need to work. Move.

00:27:51.130 --> 00:27:52.920
[Add the noodle garnishes] [Again and again]

00:27:53.570 --> 00:27:57.340
[Infinite Chore Hell]

00:27:57.770 --> 00:27:59.240
[Myungsoo, you're doing a great job!]

00:27:59.520 --> 00:27:59.880
[Mr. 10 Jobs survives]

00:27:59.880 --> 00:28:01.620
It's not like I did everything.

00:28:02.310 --> 00:28:03.300
4 beef patties are ready.

00:28:03.300 --> 00:28:03.520
OK. Thank you.

00:28:03.520 --> 00:28:05.080
[(Passes on the beef patties)]

00:28:05.350 --> 00:28:05.460
Put it here, and here.

00:28:05.460 --> 00:28:08.400
[Finishes 4 beef patties in that time too]

00:28:08.680 --> 00:28:08.950
-Is it done? -Yes.

00:28:08.950 --> 00:28:13.180
[Continues cooking the remaining 3 beef patties]

00:28:13.400 --> 00:28:15.160
[Huh? Wait a minute.]

00:28:15.340 --> 00:28:16.100
[Namno checks the beef patties closely]

00:28:16.100 --> 00:28:16.820
This is...

00:28:18.420 --> 00:28:18.820
[Overcooked beef patties]

00:28:18.820 --> 00:28:20.020
Are they overcooked?

00:28:20.370 --> 00:28:23.490
Yeah. Remove these and make 3 new ones.

00:28:25.760 --> 00:28:28.630
[Has to make the 3 beef patties again]

00:28:29.010 --> 00:28:29.550
It's OK.

00:28:30.690 --> 00:28:32.890
[Yoon Namno: They get burnt easily
because of the soy sauce.]

00:28:33.620 --> 00:28:34.790
[Jung Hae-in: I should use low heat, right?]

00:28:34.790 --> 00:28:35.710
Use low heat.

00:28:36.370 --> 00:28:36.550
Are they burnt?

00:28:36.550 --> 00:28:37.360
[Hae-in face turns stiff
after making another mistake]

00:28:37.360 --> 00:28:39.200
A little. But I like it like this.

00:28:40.850 --> 00:28:42.760
[Yoon Namno: We'll eat these burnt ones.]

00:28:42.760 --> 00:28:43.370
OK.

00:28:43.610 --> 00:28:43.760
Put this here, and here.

00:28:43.760 --> 00:28:47.040
[4 sets have been finished]

00:28:47.400 --> 00:28:47.920
[Sends out the 4 sets first]

00:28:47.920 --> 00:28:51.320
4 servings are out.
Please come forward to collect your food.

00:28:52.530 --> 00:28:56.920
[A nutritious meal for the exhausted men!]

00:28:57.200 --> 00:28:57.890
[Wow.]

00:28:58.960 --> 00:29:00.210
-This isn't supper...
-Wow, there are Dubai chewy cookies.

00:29:00.210 --> 00:29:01.690
-What? Dubai chewy cookies? -Dubai chewy cookies!

00:29:01.690 --> 00:29:03.150
-Dubai chewy cookies. -Dubai chewy cookies.

00:29:03.150 --> 00:29:04.170
[Can we eat this?]

00:29:04.170 --> 00:29:05.380
Is this really the Dubai chewy cookie?

00:29:05.380 --> 00:29:08.560
[I'm glad I came to Bucheon Fire Station.]

00:29:08.890 --> 00:29:10.060
[Luckily we're on duty today!]

