Please come forward to collect your food.

00:31:08.330 --> 00:31:09.590
Thank you for the food.

00:31:09.730 --> 00:31:10.770
-Let's eat. -Let's eat.

00:31:10.770 --> 00:31:12.680
-Let's eat. -Enjoy.

00:31:13.530 --> 00:31:17.210
[Will the 2nd batch, the rescue team members,
