Elbow grease!

00:39:02.520 --> 00:39:04.340
[Haha]

00:39:04.670 --> 00:39:05.930
[How are we doing so well?]

00:39:05.930 --> 00:39:06.840
I know.

00:39:07.370 --> 00:39:07.710
We're really becoming a team.

00:39:07.710 --> 00:39:08.510
[Continuously improving teamwork]

00:39:08.510 --> 00:39:10.730
