01:01:57.080 --> 01:01:59.500
[She's very precious to me]

01:02:01.310 --> 01:02:04.590
[Octopus, Boyoung; Dolphin, Taehyun]

01:02:04.590 --> 01:02:07.870
[Seal, Kang Hoon; Shrimp, Kwanghee; Crab, Sunbin]

01:02:07.980 --> 01:02:08.010
[Theme of Manito's Gift: Support]

01:02:08.010 --> 01:02:11.170
