01:02:12.070 --> 01:02:13.030
[Support?]

01:02:13.030 --> 01:02:13.800
Support.

01:02:14.170 --> 01:02:14.570
Thank you.

01:02:14.570 --> 01:02:17.320
[To bring strength to your Manito]

01:02:17.460 --> 01:02:20.170
[A gift of support]

01:02:22.120 --> 01:02:23.820
[Park Boyoung: What kind of support does Dad]

01:02:23.820 --> 01:02:25.530
[Need these days?]

01:02:28.460 --> 01:02:29.630
[In my opinion]

01:02:30.060 --> 01:02:33.630
[Something you can put on the desk]

01:02:33.750 --> 01:02:35.610
[Just like the old-time fathers]

01:02:35.730 --> 01:02:37.190
[I want to make]

01:02:37.330 --> 01:02:38.960
