01:02:50.210 --> 01:02:51.380
[I'm OK]

01:02:51.380 --> 01:02:51.690
It's okay.

01:02:51.690 --> 01:02:53.730
[Mr. Cha refuses in advance]

01:02:54.360 --> 01:02:58.450
[Park Boyoung: I'll call Insung, the co-CEO.

01:02:59.200 --> 01:03:00.690
[Ah!]

01:03:01.780 --> 01:03:04.680
[Park Boyoung: Hello. This is Boyoung.]

01:03:04.770 --> 01:03:06.650
