01:03:07.160 --> 01:03:07.200
[Greetings full of love]

01:03:07.200 --> 01:03:07.920
No, I'm on a show right now.

01:03:07.920 --> 01:03:09.770
-I'm shooting. -What is it?

01:03:10.490 --> 01:03:13.450
[Park Boyoung: Taehyun became my Manito.]

01:03:13.510 --> 01:03:16.500
[Park Boyoung: I need to give him a gift of support.]

01:03:16.590 --> 01:03:19.470
[Park Boyoung: Didn't he set off as a CEO?

01:03:19.670 --> 01:03:21.290
[Does he need anything?]

01:03:21.290 --> 01:03:22.910
[Do you have a seat for the boss?]

01:03:23.050 --> 01:03:25.580
[No, we don't have specific seats]

01:03:25.700 --> 01:03:26.900
[What?]

01:03:27.380 --> 01:03:28.280
[Unexpected venue conditions]

01:03:28.280 --> 01:03:29.120
I wanted to customize a nameplate.

01:03:29.120 --> 01:03:30.870
[I wanted to customize a nameplate]

01:03:31.320 --> 01:03:34.870
[Zo Insung: If it's the nameplate from you]

01:03:34.960 --> 01:03:37.210
[From Taehyun's and my perspectives]

01:03:37.320 --> 01:03:39.420
[It would be meaningful. (=I want one, too.)]

01:03:39.640 --> 01:03:43.020
[Mentioned himself subtly] [Do you have a seal?]

01:03:43.140 --> 01:03:44.720
[Zo Insung: Ah, the seal is good, too.]

01:03:44.720 --> 01:03:45.680
Ah, seal.

01:03:45.730 --> 01:03:46.580
[But we...]

01:03:46.680 --> 01:03:50.270
