01:03:50.390 --> 01:03:52.100
[So I don't think we need a seal.]

01:03:52.640 --> 01:03:55.050
[You have to sign the contract, right?]

01:03:55.050 --> 01:03:57.470
[That's right]

01:03:57.580 --> 01:03:58.100
[Adding the seal]

01:03:58.100 --> 01:03:59.610
Thank you.

01:04:01.950 --> 01:04:04.290
