01:04:11.310 --> 01:04:12.820
I really want to make a nameplate.

01:04:12.820 --> 01:04:14.060
Hello.

01:04:14.930 --> 01:04:16.460
Hello, this is the seal store.

01:04:16.460 --> 01:04:19.250
[Hello, sir. I have a question.]

01:04:19.730 --> 01:04:20.380
Can I customize a shell inlaid nameplate?

01:04:20.380 --> 01:04:21.880
