01:04:30.830 --> 01:04:32.930
[Up to receipt of the delivery.]

01:04:34.040 --> 01:04:36.700
[A week? Thank you]

01:04:36.700 --> 01:04:38.100
I'll call you if I need it.

01:04:38.220 --> 01:04:40.690
[Boss: When do you need it?] [Today.]

01:04:40.790 --> 01:04:42.710
[Boss: I can't finish a shell nameplate today.]

01:04:42.710 --> 01:04:44.560
[Really?]

01:04:44.560 --> 01:04:45.920
Thank you.

01:04:45.920 --> 01:04:46.750
Okay.

01:04:48.150 --> 01:04:49.050
[CEO: Cha Taehyun]

01:04:50.310 --> 01:04:51.620
