01:04:51.620 --> 01:04:52.830
Wait.

01:04:52.830 --> 01:04:53.340
It's so hard.

01:04:53.340 --> 01:04:56.530
[Thinking about what to do with the nameplate]

01:04:56.660 --> 01:04:57.380
