01:04:57.380 --> 01:04:58.770
Hoon?

01:05:00.700 --> 01:05:03.430
[Disdress is over] [How about start with food?]

01:05:03.560 --> 01:05:05.540
[Cha Taehyun: What do they have over at Rodeo?]

01:05:05.550 --> 01:05:07.780
[Cha Taehyun: There's a tart restaurant.]

01:05:08.330 --> 01:05:12.300
