01:05:12.640 --> 01:05:12.990
Just buy this for him.

01:05:12.990 --> 01:05:14.650
[The first gift is tart]

01:05:14.650 --> 01:05:16.320
[It doesn't matter if he likes it]

01:05:16.410 --> 01:05:16.710
