01:05:16.710 --> 01:05:19.220
[Decide quickly after a short thought]

01:05:19.370 --> 01:05:20.850
[Then!]

01:05:21.530 --> 01:05:24.010
[I'll make a nameplate for him myself]

01:05:24.400 --> 01:05:25.510
[Like father, like daughter]

01:05:25.510 --> 01:05:26.620
