01:05:32.840 --> 01:05:35.850
[Make nameplates with the welcome kit]

01:05:35.850 --> 01:05:37.110
I think it can stand up.

01:05:37.280 --> 01:05:38.710
[Oh!]

01:05:38.940 --> 01:05:39.460
Let's get the seal made first.

01:05:39.460 --> 01:05:40.920
[Decided to buy the seal first]

01:05:40.920 --> 01:05:41.910
Seal.

01:05:42.870 --> 01:05:43.110
The clerk is very kind.

01:05:43.110 --> 01:05:44.260
[Found a nearby seal store]

01:05:44.260 --> 01:05:45.920
It's written in the comments.

01:05:47.180 --> 01:05:47.260
I'll get going then.

01:05:47.260 --> 01:05:49.170
[While the daughter goes to buy the gift]

01:05:49.170 --> 01:05:50.370
Fighting!

01:05:51.580 --> 01:05:51.590
[Meanwhile, the Dad wanna wake up his real daughter]

01:05:51.590 --> 01:05:53.000
Let mr wake my daughter up first.

01:05:53.000 --> 01:05:55.400
Why isn't she up? It's 11 o'clock!

01:05:55.400 --> 01:05:59.050
[Cha Taehyun: She should be up. It's 11:30!]

01:05:59.390 --> 01:06:00.700
[His daughter sleeps in as it's vacation that time]

01:06:00.700 --> 01:06:03.190
I wonder how a person could sleep so much.

01:06:03.930 --> 01:06:04.530
[Taeeun picks up the phone anyway]

01:06:04.530 --> 01:06:05.290
Taeeun.

01:06:07.030 --> 01:06:09.070
[Cha Taehyun: Taeeun, what's your schedule today?]

01:06:09.190 --> 01:06:10.860
[What time are you going to school?]

01:06:11.170 --> 01:06:13.540
[Half asleep] [I'm going...at 1...]

01:06:13.660 --> 01:06:15.050
[At 1?]

01:06:15.580 --> 01:06:17.580
[Cha Taehyun: You're going to school at 1. And then?]

01:06:17.770 --> 01:06:21.730
[Taehyun's daughter: 4:30...] [Cha Taehyun: Why are you so busy?]

01:06:22.280 --> 01:06:22.300
Okay.

01:06:22.300 --> 01:06:25.960
[The call is over]

01:06:26.970 --> 01:06:27.040
[Buy the gift first]

01:06:27.040 --> 01:06:28.170
Let's go shop first.

01:06:29.390 --> 01:06:29.660
[Plan 1: Buy egg tarts]

01:06:29.660 --> 01:06:31.190
Let's go get some egg tarts.

01:06:34.190 --> 01:06:37.510
[Cha Taehyun: Taeeun goes to cram school at 1.]

01:06:37.650 --> 01:06:40.890
[Plan 2: Get ready for cram school and bring along the gift]

01:06:40.940 --> 01:06:41.010
