01:06:41.010 --> 01:06:44.190
[Plan 3: Taeeun delivers the gift for Taehyun]

01:06:44.440 --> 01:06:45.320
Let's go.

01:06:46.600 --> 01:06:46.750
It's pretty urgent.

01:06:46.750 --> 01:06:49.800
[Let's go buy desserts first]

01:06:50.130 --> 01:06:55.100
[Cha Taehyun: Hoon hasn't met Taeeun yet, so he wouldn't know it's me.]

01:06:55.620 --> 01:06:56.450
[Checking follows on SNS]
[To see if he and Kwanghee know anyone in common]

01:06:56.450 --> 01:06:58.640
Do we have any mutual friends?

01:07:02.440 --> 01:07:04.060
[Well...]

01:07:04.510 --> 01:07:06.990
[I don't know many people...] [Introvert]

01:07:06.990 --> 01:07:08.450
There can't be an overlap.

01:07:09.890 --> 01:07:14.010
[Starting to look Manito up on YouTube] [Focused]

01:07:17.910 --> 01:07:20.360
[He does landscaping?]

01:07:20.470 --> 01:07:21.380
Wait a second!

01:07:22.020 --> 01:07:24.000
[Kang Hoon: There are places like that in Gangnam, right?]

01:07:24.150 --> 01:07:25.980
[There are flower markets, right?]

01:07:26.080 --> 01:07:28.600
[I want to give him flowers!]

01:07:28.840 --> 01:07:31.200
[Kang Hoon: But flowers as the first gift...]

01:07:31.350 --> 01:07:35.010
[Giving a guy flowers... Haha.]

01:07:36.120 --> 01:07:37.320
[It's a good thing though... Haha.]

01:07:37.320 --> 01:07:38.120
When you receive flowers,

01:07:38.120 --> 01:07:38.680
it feels like the start of a happy new day.

01:07:38.680 --> 01:07:40.640
[Giving him flowers means showing support for his day]

01:07:40.640 --> 01:07:41.930
That kind of feeling.

01:07:43.880 --> 01:07:45.440
[Now let's write the letter...]

01:07:45.690 --> 01:07:45.820
[The letter that goes with the flowers]

01:07:45.820 --> 01:07:47.900
Let's write the letter.

01:07:49.840 --> 01:07:50.520
To...

01:07:52.010 --> 01:07:59.840
[I heard you're into landscaping. And I like that about you.] [Wait.]

01:07:59.840 --> 01:08:01.780
Wait, this feeling.

01:08:01.780 --> 01:08:02.660
Wait, this feeling.

01:08:02.660 --> 01:08:04.740
[Throwing out the pen]

01:08:06.040 --> 01:08:07.910
[It feels like we're dating. Wait.]

01:08:08.020 --> 01:08:09.710
[Imaginary relationship] [I'll write it seriously]

01:08:09.710 --> 01:08:11.600
I'll write it seriously.

01:08:14.530 --> 01:08:18.160
Yours, Sea Dog.

01:08:19.040 --> 01:08:23.520
[Kang Hoon: Done! My sincere words are what really matter.]

01:08:24.859 --> 01:08:26.580
[Wait...]

01:08:26.660 --> 01:08:28.960
