01:08:29.340 --> 01:08:30.970
[Like a box... Uh, hold on...]

01:08:30.979 --> 01:08:32.649
[Box found]

01:08:32.750 --> 01:08:33.810
[Kang Hoon: Ah, no.]

01:08:33.899 --> 01:08:35.430
