01:08:35.590 --> 01:08:35.779
[Quick makeover]

01:08:35.779 --> 01:08:36.880
Quick.

01:08:38.840 --> 01:08:42.189
[But this might make it more obvious...]

01:08:43.370 --> 01:08:46.210
[Confirming the vision]

01:08:46.930 --> 01:08:48.450
[Ah... Is the distance between the eyes too far?]

01:08:48.450 --> 01:08:49.270
But...

01:08:50.770 --> 01:08:54.960
[Testing after confirming the vision]

01:08:55.100 --> 01:08:55.380
[Hello]

01:08:55.380 --> 01:08:56.020
Like this.

01:08:56.020 --> 01:08:58.100
I have to wear it even if it looks like this.

01:08:58.100 --> 01:08:58.240
Woah! I can see through this!

01:08:58.240 --> 01:08:59.640
[Kang Hoon: Woah! I can see through this!]

01:08:59.640 --> 01:09:00.140
Okay.

01:09:00.140 --> 01:09:01.439
[Satisfied]

01:09:01.439 --> 01:09:02.380
I can do it with this.

01:09:02.380 --> 01:09:05.020
[Confidence boosted by a prop]

01:09:05.120 --> 01:09:07.160
[Oh! Wait!]

01:09:07.700 --> 01:09:10.160
[Kang Hoon: Will the shopping bag do better?]

01:09:10.890 --> 01:09:14.180
[Shopping bag found]

01:09:16.050 --> 01:09:18.300
