01:09:18.729 --> 01:09:20.420
[I need to switch to this.]

01:09:20.670 --> 01:09:23.810
[Cutting excitedly for the upgrade]

01:09:24.189 --> 01:09:26.399
[But wearing this, I'd look like a nutcase...]

01:09:26.399 --> 01:09:27.790
In Gangnam.

01:09:27.939 --> 01:09:29.330
[Oh! I can see it clearly!]

01:09:29.870 --> 01:09:32.229
[Lightness+1 Agility+1]

01:09:34.729 --> 01:09:36.370
[Ah, wait!]

01:09:36.689 --> 01:09:39.510
[Kang Hoon: To prevent accidents, I need to cut open the sides too.]

01:09:39.670 --> 01:09:41.790
[Adding side openings]

01:09:43.490 --> 01:09:45.470
[Eye showing]

01:09:47.550 --> 01:09:49.060
[All disguised]

01:09:49.060 --> 01:09:49.779
Let's go.

01:09:51.939 --> 01:09:55.450
[Taehyun after getting the egg tarts]

01:09:57.260 --> 01:09:58.400
[Taeeun!]

01:09:59.060 --> 01:10:00.960
Taeeun! Taeeun! Taeeun! Taeeun!
[Emergency call with Taeeun]

01:10:00.960 --> 01:10:02.360
-What? -Taeeun. Taeeun.

01:10:02.460 --> 01:10:03.070
[Half asleep] [What...?]

01:10:03.070 --> 01:10:04.600
Taeeun,

01:10:04.600 --> 01:10:04.820
can you do Dad a small favor right now?

01:10:04.820 --> 01:10:08.620
[Still half asleep] [What...?] [Getting straight to the point]

01:10:08.940 --> 01:10:12.700
[Cha Taehyun: Can you get ready and come with me now?]

01:10:13.100 --> 01:10:16.060
[Cha Taehyun: I only need to get you to cram school by 1, right?]

01:10:16.090 --> 01:10:16.780
Can you get ready now?

01:10:16.780 --> 01:10:18.680
[Taehyun's plan] [Using his daughter to send gifts]

01:10:18.680 --> 01:10:20.020
I'm in a hurry.

01:10:20.660 --> 01:10:22.800
[I'm almost home.] [Taehyun's daughter: What did you say?]

01:10:22.800 --> 01:10:23.620
Okay?

01:10:23.980 --> 01:10:26.180
[Dizzy] [So why should I come with you?]

01:10:26.500 --> 01:10:29.220
[I'll explain it to you on the way.]

01:10:29.620 --> 01:10:29.760
[Taehyun is arriving home]

01:10:29.760 --> 01:10:30.980
Let's stop here.

01:10:31.550 --> 01:10:32.200
Let me

01:10:33.140 --> 01:10:33.260
try to convince her.

01:10:33.260 --> 01:10:36.140
[Now] [Whether the daughter agrees to film is the key]

01:10:36.900 --> 01:10:39.460
[Off to convince her]

01:10:40.020 --> 01:10:43.980
[Before you go to school, can you drop something off for me?]

01:10:44.260 --> 01:10:46.800
[Taehyun's daughter] [Cha Taeeun: I don't even know what it is.] [Thank you!]

01:10:46.800 --> 01:10:47.480
Let's go.

01:10:48.080 --> 01:10:48.180
You woke me up.

01:10:48.180 --> 01:10:51.070
[Successfully got Taeeun on board]

01:10:51.070 --> 01:10:52.180
This way.

01:10:52.920 --> 01:10:53.780
I'm Sorry.

01:10:53.780 --> 01:10:54.450
[Grabbing hand and hurrying into the car]

01:10:54.450 --> 01:10:55.390
I'm Sorry.

01:10:57.180 --> 01:11:01.580
[Cha Taehyun: You and Ryuhyun, are you going to school together?] [Today? Probably!]

01:11:02.420 --> 01:11:05.700
[Cha Taehyun: So today you've got cram school at 1. What time does it end?]

01:11:06.130 --> 01:11:06.420
It ends at 4. I'll have free time until 4:30.

01:11:06.420 --> 01:11:09.430
[School schedule]
[13:00-16:00 Math]
[16:00-16:30 Free time]
[16:30-17:30 English]

01:11:09.430 --> 01:11:11.830
