01:11:11.830 --> 01:11:13.260
From 4:30 to 5:30.

01:11:13.650 --> 01:11:14.220
-Get in the car. -I don't even know what I'm supposed to do.

01:11:14.220 --> 01:11:16.470
[Handing over the first gift]

01:11:16.470 --> 01:11:19.070
I'll tell you on the way. We don't have time now.

01:11:20.100 --> 01:11:21.890
[Cha Taehyun: I need to see where he (Kang Hoon) is first.] [If he leaves, it's over...]

01:11:21.890 --> 01:11:23.220
Let's see where he went.

01:11:25.700 --> 01:11:27.780
[He's gone! Oh! What should I do?]

01:11:27.780 --> 01:11:28.780
Where is he going?

01:11:29.040 --> 01:11:29.340
Wait.

01:11:29.340 --> 01:11:29.760
[Sea Dog's movement spotted]

01:11:29.760 --> 01:11:31.730
He's moving.

01:11:32.540 --> 01:11:33.020
Hello.

01:11:33.020 --> 01:11:34.360
[When Taehyun is picking up Taeeun] [Kang Hoon is getting flowers]

01:11:34.360 --> 01:11:36.420
I placed an order for the hydrangeas.

01:11:37.070 --> 01:11:38.000
It's pretty.

01:11:38.000 --> 01:11:39.760
-Thank you. -Thank you.

01:11:39.760 --> 01:11:40.970
Bye.

01:11:42.800 --> 01:11:43.640
Okay.

01:11:44.500 --> 01:11:46.780
[This is more... Haha.]

01:11:47.570 --> 01:11:47.660
It feels like a gift for a lover.

01:11:47.660 --> 01:11:52.300
