the color red and Taehyun's support]

01:23:28.370 --> 01:23:29.830
I was reminded of that.

01:23:33.340 --> 01:23:35.460
[Shop Owner: It's done.]

01:23:35.700 --> 01:23:37.540
[Do you want to try it?]

01:23:37.940 --> 01:23:38.130
[Presses hard]

01:23:38.130 --> 01:23:38.990
Left and right.

01:23:39.780 --> 01:23:40.050
[Cha Taehyun]

01:23:40.050 --> 01:23:40.910
It's too light.

01:23:43.380 --> 01:23:43.900
I'm so satisfied with the first gift.

01:23:43.900 --> 01:23:46.290
[Procures the first gift filled with her support]

01:23:46.290 --> 01:23:47.890
Thank you, sir.

01:23:48.620 --> 01:23:50.300
[She's also thinking about
how to show Boyoung support]

01:23:50.300 --> 01:23:52.350
This will be a chance to repay her.

01:23:52.350 --> 01:23:52.900
Because

01:23:52.900 --> 01:23:55.950
my birthday's in January, and Boyoung

01:23:55.960 --> 01:23:57.300
prepared a surprise for me.

01:23:57.300 --> 01:24:00.690
She left a birthday gift in front of my house.

01:24:00.740 --> 01:24:02.100
[Lee Sunbin: I've gotten a gift first.]

01:24:02.100 --> 01:24:05.060
[Lee Sunbin: I've basically
received a Manito gift.]

01:24:09.060 --> 01:24:13.300
[It's not a bad idea
to celebrate her birthday in advance.]

01:24:13.470 --> 01:24:13.780
Like a birthday celebration revenge.

01:24:13.780 --> 01:24:16.860
[Boyoung's birthday is in 5 days,
from the day of this shoot]

01:24:17.300 --> 01:24:20.980
[Sunbin's plan:
an early birthday party for Boyoung]

01:24:21.190 --> 01:24:21.820
Wait, I'll write a letter first.

01:24:21.820 --> 01:24:24.000
[Step 1: Figure out what she likes]

01:24:24.000 --> 01:24:24.340
Food...

01:24:24.340 --> 01:24:27.120
[Reference questions for the birthday party]

01:24:27.120 --> 01:24:28.420
she likes.

01:24:28.420 --> 01:24:28.940
Songs she likes.

01:24:28.940 --> 01:24:33.100
[To prevent handwriting recognition,
she writes with her left hand]

01:24:33.380 --> 01:24:33.740
What do you think?

01:24:33.740 --> 01:24:35.060
[A preference questionnaire
to be given to Boyoung]

01:24:35.060 --> 01:24:37.780
My little princess, wait for me.

01:24:38.700 --> 01:24:41.100
[Thinking of other ideas
after finishing the questionnaire]

01:24:41.260 --> 01:24:41.660
Record all the preparations I make
while preparing for her gifts in a camera,

01:24:41.660 --> 01:24:45.320
[Step 2: Gift her a camera which records
the process of the Manito mission]

01:24:45.320 --> 01:24:47.240
and gift her the camera.

01:24:47.340 --> 01:24:48.500
[It'll be totally...]

01:24:48.500 --> 01:24:50.380
[Lee Sunbin: After this event, it'd still linger.]

01:24:50.380 --> 01:24:52.900
[Lee Sunbin: It's a surprise
so that she'll be moved once again.]

01:24:53.220 --> 01:24:55.930
I'm going to be the Choi Soojong

01:24:55.930 --> 01:24:56.180
of the Manito world.

01:24:56.180 --> 01:25:00.100
[Manito romantic: Bin-Soojong]

01:25:00.540 --> 01:25:02.260
[Where is she right now?]

01:25:02.260 --> 01:25:04.860
[Oh? Wait, where's this?]

01:25:05.340 --> 01:25:07.460
[Please get off.]

01:25:08.180 --> 01:25:08.400
[Big strides as she goes to eat]

01:25:08.400 --> 01:25:10.910
Let's go eat.

01:25:11.740 --> 01:25:12.080
[Heading to the restaurant Boyoung is at]

01:25:12.080 --> 01:25:13.810
Why'd she move slightly?

01:25:14.780 --> 01:25:17.100
[Lee Sunbin: Let's go. I think she went
to a BBQ restaurant for food.]

01:25:17.780 --> 01:25:20.460
[Lee Sunbin: I think (Boyoung) has
ordered raw beef bibimbap now.]

01:25:20.940 --> 01:25:22.860
[(Correct) We'll all have raw beef bibimbap.]

01:25:22.860 --> 01:25:22.910
[Certified bestie]

01:25:22.910 --> 01:25:25.040
She'll definitely have raw beef bibimbap.

01:25:25.040 --> 01:25:26.510
Thank you.

01:25:26.510 --> 01:25:26.540
Oh no. Oh no.

01:25:26.540 --> 01:25:30.020
[Arrived at the destination]

01:25:30.940 --> 01:25:32.900
[Ah, my heart's beating so fast...]

01:25:33.500 --> 01:25:34.350
[Moving with nervousness]

01:25:34.350 --> 01:25:36.130
Will she recognize me?

01:25:37.260 --> 01:25:39.460
[Lee Sunbin: (Boyoung)
is inside there right now.]

01:25:41.900 --> 01:25:43.700
[Shaking]

01:25:44.100 --> 01:25:46.340
[Digs in with a relaxed mind]

01:25:51.660 --> 01:25:55.540
[Closing in to the 2nd floor]

01:26:01.500 --> 01:26:02.820
[Lee Sunbin: Hello.]

01:26:02.820 --> 01:26:05.460
[Lee Sunbin: Excuse me. I'm shooting a show.]

01:26:05.460 --> 01:26:07.700
[Lee Sunbin: Can I hide here?]
[Here →]

01:26:07.700 --> 01:26:08.260
OK, wait.

01:26:08.260 --> 01:26:11.060
[Meticulously gets permission
to use the room as a hideout]
[Here →]

01:26:11.790 --> 01:26:11.900
They won't come now, right?

01:26:11.900 --> 01:26:13.020
[Whoosh]

01:26:13.020 --> 01:26:15.140
[Becoming alert after hearing noise behind her]

01:26:15.140 --> 01:26:16.580
[Crew: What will you do if your Manito comes?]

01:26:16.580 --> 01:26:17.700
[Crew: Will you rush out?]

01:26:17.700 --> 01:26:20.460
[Park Boyoung: I'm curious,
but there are stairs. It's dangerous.]

01:26:20.700 --> 01:26:23.500
[What if they fall while running away?]

01:26:23.820 --> 01:26:28.020
[Park Boyoung]

01:26:29.620 --> 01:26:31.700
[Whoosh]

01:26:35.220 --> 01:26:38.180
[Carefully leaves her a gift, just one door away]

01:26:39.060 --> 01:26:40.860
[Knock, knock]

01:26:41.980 --> 01:26:44.060
[Ah, they left something and fled!]

01:26:45.820 --> 01:26:47.280
[Lee Sunbin hides in her hideout]

01:26:47.280 --> 01:26:48.940
They left something and fled!

01:26:49.300 --> 01:26:49.800
[Ah!]

01:26:52.900 --> 01:26:56.340
[Lee Sunbin]

01:26:56.460 --> 01:27:00.340
[Ha... This is driving me crazy.]

01:27:01.380 --> 01:27:03.820
[Wait, I didn't even
catch a glimpse of their back!]

01:27:04.780 --> 01:27:07.160
[Unlike what she said, she's chasing quickly]

01:27:07.160 --> 01:27:08.480
Very...

01:27:09.180 --> 01:27:11.180
[Who is it?]

01:27:13.220 --> 01:27:15.180
[Poking her head out]

01:27:16.020 --> 01:27:17.820
[Ah...]

01:27:18.660 --> 01:27:22.540
[Lee Sunbin]
[Park Boyoung: They're that fast?]

01:27:23.500 --> 01:27:26.580
[Suspicious because
they erased their trace so quickly]

01:27:28.180 --> 01:27:29.380
[No, because...]

01:27:29.460 --> 01:27:29.820
But...

01:27:29.820 --> 01:27:32.340
[(Picks up the gift) No, because...]

01:27:32.860 --> 01:27:35.540
[Park Boyoung: After knocking and leaving...]

01:27:36.180 --> 01:27:38.580
[They couldn't have went so far.]

01:27:39.180 --> 01:27:40.460
[(Whispers) Drop your camera.]

01:27:40.460 --> 01:27:42.100
[(Whispers) Just sit on the floor.]

01:27:42.220 --> 01:27:43.820
[Intuitively searches the next room]

01:27:49.260 --> 01:27:50.660
[Eh?]

01:27:52.260 --> 01:27:54.060
[Smiles]

01:27:55.300 --> 01:27:57.500
[(Whispers) Oh no, Boyoung is coming!]

01:27:58.100 --> 01:28:01.020
[Ready to open all the rooms]

01:28:14.180 --> 01:28:16.420
What's this darn Octopus doing?

01:28:16.500 --> 01:28:19.460
[Only my Pufferfish hasn't received a gift!]

01:28:19.780 --> 01:28:19.940
I support you, Boss Cha Taehyun.

01:28:19.940 --> 01:28:22.340
[Starts making a nameplate for Taehyun]

01:28:22.380 --> 01:28:23.380
[Hoo...]

01:28:24.140 --> 01:28:25.860
[Oh no, it's crooked. No!]

01:28:25.860 --> 01:28:26.660
[It tore off.]

01:28:26.660 --> 01:28:27.060
[Lovely Boyoung is swamped with hardship]

01:28:27.060 --> 01:28:28.060
Ha... What should I do?

01:28:28.060 --> 01:28:28.080
[Asks for help again with the good-natured Insung
(T/N: "Insung" and "good-natured" are homonyms)]

01:28:28.080 --> 01:28:29.150
Insung-oppa!

01:28:29.150 --> 01:28:30.330
Who is it? Who's bullying you?

01:28:30.330 --> 01:28:30.580
What should I do?

01:28:30.580 --> 01:28:32.900
[Can she please Taehyun?]
[(Don't let me catch you)]

01:28:32.900 --> 01:28:34.140
[I'm known as a great chaser.]

01:28:34.140 --> 01:28:35.380
[Please look forward to my performance.]

01:28:35.380 --> 01:28:36.540
[Let's catch Seal today.]

01:28:36.540 --> 01:28:38.420
[Seal!] [Seal!] [Seal!]

01:28:38.420 --> 01:28:38.460
-Wait! -Seal, be careful!

01:28:38.460 --> 01:28:40.340
[Properly begins to toy with Seal]

01:28:40.340 --> 01:28:42.180
I'll count to 10 so you can flee!

01:28:42.180 --> 01:28:45.380
Hide well, or I might see your Seal tail.

01:28:45.380 --> 01:28:46.340
[Seal, have you run away?]

01:28:46.480 --> 01:28:46.980
[Oh my!]

01:28:46.980 --> 01:28:49.540
[Seal who is... a little clumsy...]

01:28:49.540 --> 01:28:50.260
[Ah, I'm so angry!]

01:28:50.260 --> 01:28:51.140
[Ah, I'm so angry!]

01:28:51.140 --> 01:28:51.820
[I'm so angry.]

01:28:51.820 --> 01:28:51.890
[Kang Hoon]

01:28:51.890 --> 01:28:52.320
Ugh, I'm really angry.

01:28:52.320 --> 01:28:53.620
[Anger Kang]

01:28:53.820 --> 01:28:55.110
[I don't want to give gifts anymore...]

01:28:55.110 --> 01:28:56.440
I can't do this anymore.

01:28:57.740 --> 01:28:59.620
[Hello, this is a yoga project (?)]

01:28:59.680 --> 01:28:59.700
Hello.

01:28:59.700 --> 01:29:00.520
[Why is there a horse?]

01:29:00.520 --> 01:29:01.260
Hello.

01:29:01.260 --> 01:29:02.320
Hello!
[It's Sunbin in a horse fursuit]

01:29:02.320 --> 01:29:04.580
I'm right in front of her, but she has no clue.

01:29:04.580 --> 01:29:05.500
[(Full of anticipation)
Does she not know it's me?]

01:29:05.500 --> 01:29:07.900
[(She knows) Are you my Manito?]

01:29:07.900 --> 01:29:09.100
[N... No]

01:29:09.100 --> 01:29:10.180
[Good luck, my Manito!]

01:29:10.210 --> 01:29:11.300
I suddenly regret it.

01:29:11.300 --> 01:29:12.190
[Has the Horse Manito's plan failed?]

01:29:12.190 --> 01:29:13.280
Is this OK?

01:29:14.140 --> 01:29:14.900
[Transform!]

01:29:14.900 --> 01:29:15.620
[Here!]

01:29:15.620 --> 01:29:16.980
[What is that?]

01:29:17.140 --> 01:29:18.300
[Why is there another fursuit!]

01:29:18.300 --> 01:29:19.540
[Isn't it thrilling?]

01:29:19.540 --> 01:29:20.820
[Wow, I got a gift!]

01:29:20.820 --> 01:29:22.060
[Wow, this is crazy.]

01:29:22.180 --> 01:29:24.820
[To make Sun-bean happy,
Kwang-pea will go anywhere]

01:29:25.140 --> 01:29:26.140
[OK! It's do or die!]

01:29:26.460 --> 01:29:27.020
[Shrimp! Shrimp!]

01:29:27.200 --> 01:29:27.540
Gosh, you scared me!

01:29:27.540 --> 01:29:28.320
[The Manitos have become more daring (?)]

01:29:28.320 --> 01:29:28.920
Wait, wait!

01:29:28.920 --> 01:29:30.100
-Just once! Let me off just once! -Who are you?

01:29:30.100 --> 01:29:30.410
[The Manitos have become more daring (?)]

01:29:30.410 --> 01:29:31.860
-Please let me off! Just this once! -Tell me!

01:29:31.860 --> 01:29:33.460
[Leave the gift and run!]

01:29:35.300 --> 01:29:36.620
[Ah! So exciting!]

01:29:36.620 --> 01:29:39.020
[Manito climax]

01:29:39.020 --> 01:29:40.420
[My agents (?) are amazing!]

01:29:40.540 --> 01:29:42.680
[This Secret Manito mission is at Ulsan Station]

01:29:42.680 --> 01:29:44.540
A workshop for 3 days and 2 nights.

01:29:45.280 --> 01:29:45.700
There's no way!

01:29:45.700 --> 01:29:46.540
[The Manito Speculation Train departs]

01:29:46.540 --> 01:29:48.420
I sent a text saying someone was there!

01:29:48.420 --> 01:29:50.080
I'll keep my mouth shut today.

01:29:50.910 --> 01:29:51.020
How did we all get together?

01:29:51.020 --> 01:29:52.180
[The Manito Club members have assembled]

01:29:52.180 --> 01:29:53.490
We're all together now.

01:29:53.490 --> 01:29:53.620
I'm excited and looking forward to it.

01:29:53.620 --> 01:29:55.000
[Time for the exciting Ulsan workshop!]

01:29:55.000 --> 01:29:56.430
I'm so touched at the end.